oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Own or shared silage feeding place for dairy cows?
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Raussi, S.
Mäntysaari, P.
Jauhiainen, L.
Siivonen, J.
Tuomisto, L.
Räsänen, K.
Rinne, M.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Animal husbandry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: We studied behaviour, silage eating and milk production of cows when every animal had an own silage feeding place and when the feeding place was shared with two other cows.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Raussi, S.; Mäntysaari, P.; Jauhiainen, L.; Siivonen, J.; Tuomisto, L.; Räsänen, K. and Rinne, M. (2010) Own or shared silage feeding place for dairy cows? In: Proceedings of the 22nd Nordic symposium of the International Society for Applied Ethology, Finnish Society for Applied Ethology, p. 28.
